    public class OpenReferences.OpenEntityReferences
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the open references of one entity. Can be used to transfer open references from one model to another (see OpenReferences.getOpenReferences(IEntity) and OpenReferences.addOpenReferences(IEntity, OpenEntityReferences))

      • getNames

        public java.util.Set<java.lang.String> getNames()
        Returns a Set containing the names of all contained open references.

        The returned set is a copy of the internal structure, thus modifications to the containing OpenReferences object are possible also during iterating the returned set.
        Returns:
        a Set containing the names of all contained open references

      • getPaths

        public java.util.List<java.lang.String> getPaths(java.lang.String referenceName)
        Returns a List containing the paths of all open references of the given name in the order they were added.

        The returned list is a copy of the internal structure, thus modifications to the containing OpenReferences object are possible also during iterating the returned list.
        Parameters:
        referenceName - the name of the references that shall be returned
        Returns:
        a List containing the paths of all open references of the given name
